</p>

</div>
<div id="fn" class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-02-02-02-0204-fn-0001-ptr" id="GEWN-02-02-02-0204-fn-0001">1</a>

   <p>GW discussed all of the points he raised in this letter in his letter of the same date to Dinwiddie.</p>

</div>
